'''FM eSports''' is a British team formed from the original members of the  '''Animate eSports''' roster. The organization FM eSports is highly regarded in the FPS scene, having previously only had an amateur team represent them in League of Legends they look to make a big name for themselves with the old Animate eSports roster in 2014.

